title: Why is the pixel 5 main camera so blurry compared to other pixels?
content:
Myself and many others are experiencing blurry photos on the pixel 5 main sensor while other pixels have crisp sharp photos.

Why?

This youtube video shows what I am talking about . Just look at the difference when they zoom in on the identical photos.. the 4a and 4XL are crisp and the 5 is blurry.

https://youtu.be/_oNQrWWarJY
